snippet.title: Miniatures - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello gamers! I would like to announce you my cozy puzzle game Miniatures! 

In this journey, you're tasked with solving puzzles of miniature-style illustrations to create cities by fitting blocks, making paths by aligning roads & rivers and reanimating landmarks by matching pieces.

WISHLIST NOW! : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2832810/Miniatures/

Credits

Song: "Droplets of Dew"  from ZapSplat (zapsplat.com)
